{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================
  ROLETA ESTRATÉGICA v11.0 — ARRAIÁ DA GRAÇA (Clean Premium+)
  ============================================================
  • MOTOR v8/v9/v10 INTACTO: gatilhos, UTMify, last-chance, captura
    de lead, storage, pesos de prêmio, social proof, timer.
    NENHUMA lógica de funil foi alterada.

  • RESKIN CLEAN PREMIUM (mantido da v10):
    - Cormorant Garamond (display) + Jost (UI)
    - Paleta arraiá dessaturada (brasa · dourado · linho)
    - Bandeirinhas finas em 3 tons · emoji mínimo · ícones SVG
    - Tokens de cor no topo (.gr-roleta) → retematizar em 6 linhas
    - prefers-reduced-motion respeitado

  • NOVIDADES v11 (cirúrgicas, marcadas com [v11] — fáceis de reverter):
    1. [v11] CORREÇÃO DE TIMING reduced-motion: resultado aparece quando
       a roda realmente para (2.4s) e não com 2.5s de tela morta.
       Tempo de giro centralizado em SPIN_MS.
    2. [v11] ACESSIBILIDADE DE FOCO: trap de Tab dentro do modal, foco
       inicial no primeiro campo e devolução do foco ao fechar.
    3. [v11] SCROLL-LOCK iOS de verdade (position:fixed + restauração),
       o fundo não rola mais atrás do popup no Safari mobile.
    4. [v11] aria-label nos inputs + anel de foco dourado visível
       (navegação por teclado premium).
    5. [v11] Altura do modal com dvh (barra do Safari não corta o botão).

  UTMify (igual v8/v9/v10): toda venda chega com
    utm_source=roleta · utm_medium=popup · utm_campaign=<trigger>
    utm_content=<cupom> · utm_term=<device>
  ============================================================
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if section.settings.enabled -%}

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  /* ============ TOKENS — troque aqui pra retematizar (Grassa/Cida) ============ */
  .gr-roleta {
    --gr-ground-1:#faf5ec; --gr-ground-2:#f0e6d2;
    --gr-ink:#2b1d12; --gr-ink-soft:#7c6a58;
    --gr-brasa:#b3522d; --gr-brasa-deep:#8a3a1c; --gr-brasa-soft:#cf7a4a;
    --gr-gold:#bfa05f; --gr-gold-lt:#e3cf9f; --gr-gold-dp:#9a7d3d;
    --gr-line:#e6d8bd; --gr-cream:#fffdf7; --gr-green:#4a7a52;
    --gr-serif:'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    --gr-sans:'Jost', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  }
  .gr-roleta * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }

  /* [v11] anel de foco dourado visível só para teclado (premium a11y) */
  .gr-roleta button:focus-visible,
  .gr-roleta input:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--gr-gold-dp); outline-offset: 3px; border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .gr-roleta-overlay {
    position: fixed; inset: 0;
    background: rgba(22, 14, 8, 0.84);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    z-index: 999998; display: none;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity .45s ease; padding: 18px;
  }
  .gr-roleta-overlay.is-open { display: flex; opacity: 1; }

  .gr-roleta-modal {
    position: relative; width: 100%; max-width: 432px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gr-ground-1), var(--gr-ground-2));
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 110px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
    padding: 58px 30px 36px; text-align: center;
    transform: translateY(22px) scale(.97); opacity: 0;
    transition: transform .55s cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1), opacity .45s ease;
    font-family: var(--gr-sans);
    color: var(--gr-ink); overflow: hidden;
    max-height: 96vh; max-height: 96dvh; /* [v11] dvh: Safari mobile não corta o botão */
    overflow-y: auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    border: 1px solid var(--gr-line);
  }
  .gr-roleta-overlay.is-open .gr-roleta-modal { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  /* fio fino dourado no topo (substitui o xadrez gritante) */
  .gr-roleta-modal::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; z-index: 3;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gr-brasa), var(--gr-gold) 50%, var(--gr-brasa));
  }
  /* textura de linho discreta */
  .gr-roleta-modal::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; opacity: .35; z-index: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(166,133,72,.04) 0 2px, transparent 2px 5px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(166,133,72,.03) 0 2px, transparent 2px 5px);
  }

  /* BANDEIRINHAS — finas, 3 tons, fio sutil */
  .gr-flags { position: absolute; top: 8px; left: 0; right: 0; height: 30px; z-index: 4;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-around; align-items: flex-start; pointer-events: none; padding: 0 14px; }
  .gr-flag { width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 8px solid transparent; border-right: 8px solid transparent;
    border-top: 14px solid var(--c); transform-origin: top center; position: relative;
    animation: grSway 3.4s ease-in-out infinite; filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.08)); opacity: .9; }
  .gr-flag::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: -2px; left: -14px; right: -14px; height: 1px; background: var(--gr-gold-dp); opacity: .35; z-index: -1; }
  .gr-flag:nth-child(odd) { animation-delay: .5s; }
  @keyframes grSway { 0%,100% { transform: rotate(-3deg); } 50% { transform: rotate(3deg); } }

  .gr-arraia { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gr-brasa); letter-spacing: .34em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 4px 0 10px; position: relative; z-index: 5; }
  .gr-eyebrow { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .32em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gr-ink-soft); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 500; position: relative; z-index: 5; }
  .gr-title { font-family: var(--gr-serif); font-size: 34px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--gr-ink); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -.005em; position: relative; z-index: 5; }
  .gr-title b { color: var(--gr-brasa); font-weight: 600; }
  .gr-subtitle { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gr-ink-soft); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 20px; max-width: 320px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; position: relative; z-index: 5; }

  .gr-lead-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto 20px; position: relative; z-index: 5; }
  .gr-lead-form input {
    width: 100%; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid var(--gr-line); border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 16px; color: var(--gr-ink); font-family: var(--gr-sans); background: var(--gr-cream);
    transition: border-color .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease; -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none;
  }
  .gr-lead-form input::placeholder { color: #b3a38f; }
  .gr-lead-form input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gr-gold); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(191,160,95,.14); background: #fff; }
  .gr-lead-form input.error { border-color: #b00020; background: #fff5f5; }

  .gr-wheel-wrap { position: relative; width: 300px; height: 300px; margin: 0 auto 6px; z-index: 5; }
  @media (min-width: 480px) { .gr-wheel-wrap { width: 328px; height: 328px; } }

  /* FOGUEIRA atrás da roleta — brilho suave */
  .gr-fogo { position: absolute; inset: -14px; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(207,122,74,.28), transparent 64%); animation: grFlick 2.6s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes grFlick { 0%,100% { opacity: .5; transform: scale(1); } 50% { opacity: .85; transform: scale(1.04); } }

  .gr-wheel-pointer { position: absolute; top: -6px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 26px; height: 34px; z-index: 6; filter: drop-shadow(0 3px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.35)); }

  .gr-wheel-center {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 84px; height: 84px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 32% 28%, #3a2418, #1f140f); color: var(--gr-gold-lt);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 2px;
    font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .26em; font-weight: 600; z-index: 6;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.4), inset 0 0 0 1.5px var(--gr-gold), inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.1);
    text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    animation: grCenterPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; transition: transform .15s ease;
  }
  .gr-wheel-center .gr-hat { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .gr-wheel-center .gr-hat svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
  .gr-wheel-center::after { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 6px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid rgba(191,160,95,.4); pointer-events: none; }
  .gr-wheel-center:active { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(.95); }
  .gr-wheel-center.is-spinning { animation: none; cursor: not-allowed; opacity: .92; }
  @keyframes grCenterPulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.4), inset 0 0 0 1.5px var(--gr-gold), inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.1), 0 0 0 0 rgba(207,122,74,.45); }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(0,0,0,.4), inset 0 0 0 1.5px var(--gr-gold), inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.1), 0 0 0 12px rgba(207,122,74,0); }
  }

  .gr-wheel { width: 100%; height: 100%; position: relative; z-index: 3; transition: transform 4.8s cubic-bezier(.17,.67,.16,1); filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.2)); }
  .gr-wheel-text { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .08em; }

  .gr-close { position: absolute; top: 14px; right: 14px; width: 38px; height: 38px; border: none; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; color: #b09a78; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 50%; z-index: 10; transition: color .2s ease; }
  .gr-close:hover { color: var(--gr-ink); }
  .gr-close:active { background: rgba(0,0,0,.04); }
  .gr-close svg { width: 17px; height: 17px; }

  .gr-hint { margin-top: 10px; font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 10px; color: var(--gr-ink-soft); letter-spacing: .2em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grHintBlink 2.4s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes grHintBlink { 0%, 100% { opacity: .85; } 50% { opacity: .4; } }

  .gr-screen { display: none; }
  .gr-screen.is-active { display: block; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease both; }
  @keyframes grFadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  .gr-result-stage { position: relative; padding: 8px 0 4px; margin-bottom: 10px; z-index: 5; }
  .gr-flash { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; width: 200px; height: 200px; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0);
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(227,207,159,.85) 0%, rgba(191,160,95,.35) 40%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; animation: grFlashBurst 1.2s ease-out forwards; }
  @keyframes grFlashBurst { 0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(0); opacity: 1; } 50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.4); opacity: .8; } 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(2); opacity: 0; } }

  .gr-result-icon {
    position: relative; z-index: 2; width: 80px; height: 80px; margin: 0 auto 18px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, var(--gr-gold-lt) 0%, var(--gr-gold) 52%, var(--gr-gold-dp) 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(191,160,95,.4), inset 0 2px 4px rgba(255,255,255,.3), 0 0 0 4px rgba(191,160,95,.12);
    animation: grIconWin 1.2s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) both;
  }
  .gr-result-icon svg { width: 36px; height: 36px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  @keyframes grIconWin { 0% { transform: scale(0) rotate(-300deg); opacity: 0; } 55% { transform: scale(1.2) rotate(-12deg); opacity: 1; } 78% { transform: scale(.96) rotate(6deg); } 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); } }

  .gr-result-title { font-family: var(--gr-serif); font-size: 40px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gr-ink); margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.05; position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grTitleZoom .8s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1) .3s both; }
  @keyframes grTitleZoom { 0% { transform: scale(.6); opacity: 0; } 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } }
  .gr-result-prize { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gr-ink-soft); margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 1.45; max-width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease .6s both; }

  .gr-coupon { border: 1px dashed var(--gr-gold); background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbf5e7 0%, #f2e7cf 100%); padding: 20px 16px; margin: 18px auto; max-width: 300px; border-radius: 4px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; z-index: 5; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease .8s both; }
  .gr-coupon::before, .gr-coupon::after { content: ""; position: absolute; width: 16px; height: 16px; background: var(--gr-ground-1); border-radius: 50%; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); }
  .gr-coupon::before { left: -8px; } .gr-coupon::after { right: -8px; }
  .gr-coupon-label { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gr-brasa); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
  .gr-coupon-code { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gr-ink); letter-spacing: .16em; margin-bottom: 6px; word-break: break-all; }
  .gr-coupon-min { font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 11px; color: #8a7a6c; }

  .gr-social-proof { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; margin: 12px auto 0; max-width: 300px; padding: 8px 14px; background: rgba(74,122,82,.08); border-radius: 30px; font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 11px; color: var(--gr-green); font-weight: 500; position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease 1.4s both; }
  .gr-social-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gr-green); animation: grPulseGreen 1.4s ease infinite; }
  @keyframes grPulseGreen { 0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(74,122,82,.5); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(74,122,82,0); } }

  .gr-timer { margin: 16px auto 20px; max-width: 300px; padding: 11px; background: #f6edd9; border: 1px solid var(--gr-line); border-radius: 3px; font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 12px; color: var(--gr-ink-soft); position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease 1s both; }
  .gr-timer strong { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; color: var(--gr-brasa); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: .05em; }
  .gr-timer.expired strong { color: #b00020; }

  .gr-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gr-brasa-soft) 0%, var(--gr-brasa) 55%, var(--gr-brasa-deep) 100%);
    color: #fff; border: none; padding: 17px 32px; min-height: 54px; width: 100%; max-width: 300px;
    font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: .22em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 3px;
    transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .2s ease; text-decoration: none; position: relative; overflow: hidden; z-index: 5;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(181,83,46,.32); animation: grFadeUp .5s ease 1.2s both, grBtnPulse 2.6s ease-in-out 1.6s infinite;
  }
  .gr-btn::after { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 35%, rgba(255,255,255,.22) 50%, transparent 65%); transform: translateX(-100%); animation: grBtnShine 3.4s ease infinite; pointer-events: none; }
  @keyframes grBtnShine { 0%, 65% { transform: translateX(-100%); } 100% { transform: translateX(100%); } }
  @keyframes grBtnPulse { 0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(181,83,46,.32); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(181,83,46,.55); } }
  .gr-btn:active { transform: scale(.98); }
  .gr-btn:disabled { background: #b8a890; cursor: not-allowed; animation: none; box-shadow: none; }
  .gr-btn:disabled::after { display: none; }

  .gr-gift .gr-result-icon { background: linear-gradient(140deg, #8a9663 0%, #5e6b3f 100%); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.2), inset 0 0 0 1.5px var(--gr-gold); }
  .gr-gift-badge { display: inline-block; background: #1f140f; color: var(--gr-gold); font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: .3em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 500; border: 1px solid var(--gr-gold); position: relative; z-index: 5; animation: grFadeUp .5s ease .1s both; }

  .gr-confetti-wrap { position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 999999; overflow: hidden; }
  .gr-confetti-shape { position: absolute; will-change: transform, opacity; opacity: 0; line-height: 1; }
  .gr-confetti-shape.fall { top: -40px; animation: grConfettiFall var(--dur, 4s) linear forwards; }
  @keyframes grConfettiFall { 0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) rotate(0deg); } 5% { opacity: 1; } 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(var(--dx, 0px), 110vh, 0) rotate(var(--rot, 720deg)); } }
  .gr-confetti-shape.fall.sway { animation: grConfettiFallSway var(--dur, 4s) linear forwards; }
  @keyframes grConfettiFallSway { 0% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) rotate(0deg); } 5% { opacity: 1; } 25% { transform: translate3d(40px, 25vh, 0) rotate(180deg); } 50% { transform: translate3d(-40px, 50vh, 0) rotate(360deg); } 75% { transform: translate3d(40px, 75vh, 0) rotate(540deg); } 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate3d(0, 110vh, 0) rotate(720deg); } }
  .gr-confetti-shape.burst { top: 50%; left: 50%; animation: grConfettiBurst 1.6s cubic-bezier(.2, .6, .35, 1) forwards; }
  @keyframes grConfettiBurst { 0% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(0deg) scale(0.3); } 20% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1) rotate(90deg); } 100% { opacity: 0; transform: translate(calc(-50% + var(--bx, 0px)), calc(-50% + var(--by, 0px))) rotate(var(--br, 360deg)) scale(1); } }
  .gr-cf-flag { width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 6px solid transparent; border-right: 6px solid transparent; border-top: 11px solid var(--c); }
  .gr-cf-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--c); }

  .gr-teaser { position: fixed; bottom: 18px; left: 18px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f140f, #3a2418); color: #fff; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 30px; font-family: var(--gr-sans); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .16em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; z-index: 999990; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.28); display: none; align-items: center; gap: 9px; border: 1px solid var(--gr-gold); animation: grTeaserIn .5s ease; }
  .gr-teaser.is-visible { display: inline-flex; }
  .gr-teaser:active { transform: scale(.95); }
  .gr-teaser-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gr-brasa-soft); animation: grPulse 1.6s ease infinite; }
  @keyframes grPulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: .4; } }
  @keyframes grTeaserIn { from { transform: translateY(60px); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }

  /* ============ ACESSIBILIDADE: respeita quem pede menos movimento ============ */
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .gr-flag, .gr-fogo, .gr-wheel-center, .gr-hint, .gr-btn, .gr-btn::after,
    .gr-social-dot, .gr-teaser-dot, .gr-result-icon, .gr-result-title { animation: none !important; }
    .gr-wheel { transition: transform 2.4s ease-out; } /* [v11] casa com SPIN_MS reduzido no JS */
    .gr-roleta-overlay, .gr-roleta-modal { transition: opacity .2s ease; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .gr-roleta-modal { padding: 52px 22px 26px; }
    .gr-title { font-size: 30px; }
    .gr-result-title { font-size: 34px; }
    .gr-coupon-code { font-size: 20px; }
  }
</style>

<div class="gr-roleta" id="gr-root">
  <div class="gr-roleta-overlay" id="gr-overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="gr-title">
    <div class="gr-roleta-modal">

      <div class="gr-flags" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#b3522d"></span><span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#bfa05f"></span>
        <span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#efe2c8"></span><span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#b3522d"></span>
        <span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#bfa05f"></span><span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#efe2c8"></span>
        <span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#b3522d"></span><span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#bfa05f"></span>
        <span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#efe2c8"></span><span class="gr-flag" style="--c:#b3522d"></span>
      </div>

      <button class="gr-close" id="gr-close" aria-label="Fechar">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
      </button>

      <div class="gr-screen is-active" id="gr-spin-screen">
        <div class="gr-arraia">É tempo de festa</div>
        <div class="gr-eyebrow" id="gr-eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow_text | default: 'Arraiá da Graça' }}</div>
        <h2 class="gr-title" id="gr-title">{{ section.settings.title | default: 'Gire a roleta do São João' }}</h2>
